 sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julien-baker">Julien Baker</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/torres">Torres</a>分享了他们乡村风格的首张专辑《Sugar In The Tank》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/boygenius-the-record-nme-album-of-the-year-2023-3555857"><b>Boygenius 谈《The Record》的持久力量：“我们感觉就像我们所希望的那样好”</b></a></li></ul><p>本周早些时候，两人在<i>《吉米·法伦今夜秀》中亮相</i>，给粉丝带来了惊喜，今天（12 月 13 日）分享了这首单曲，该单曲借鉴了他们在南方酷儿成长的共同经历。</p><p> Soloist 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">Boygenius</a>成员 Baker 于 10 月 5 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/julien-baker-announces-new-york-city-residency-at-webster-hall-3783426">在纽约韦伯斯特音乐厅开始了为期三晚的演出</a>，在那里她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/julien-baker-ends-new-york-gig-early-due-to-illness-confirms-new-date-with-special-guest-3800501">与 Torres 首次亮相了两首新歌</a>。然而，第二天晚上，她因生病而被迫中途离开舞台，乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lucy-dacus">露西·达克斯</a>被迫宣布演出将提前结束。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="朱利安·贝克和托雷斯：罐子里的糖|吉米·法伦主演的《今夜秀》" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HcTr10SpRhs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在调侃了这些歌曲并放弃了单曲后，一些歌迷相信一张新的乡村专辑正在制作中，尽管目前还没有任何细节，但在歌曲旁边有一个新网站，详细介绍了他们的联合巡演日期。</p><p>演出包括 3 月 27 日至 30 日的诺克斯维尔大耳朵音乐节、4 月 26 日至 27 日的 High Water 音乐节以及 5 月 15 日至 18 日的 Kilby Block Party，您可以<a href="https://julienbakerandtorres.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到更多日期和详细信息。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-julien-baker-debut-two-new-songs-in-chicago-3797594">贝克此前曾在芝加哥首演了两首新歌</a>——《Middle Children》和《High In The Basement》，这煽动了专辑的谣言。在其他地方，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-julien-baker-bring-out-bartees-strange-for-ringside-in-washington-dc-3798053">还与 Bartees Strange 一起在华盛顿特区特别演绎了“Ringside”</a> 。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DDS-pBVOZzo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C5